03:25.859 --> 03:28.132
You do know that the people
listening to the podcast

03:28.133 --> 03:30.635
in their cars won't be
able to see you, right?

03:30.636 --> 03:31.887
Very funny.

03:33.480 --> 03:34.939
- Hey.
- Hey, Eddie.

03:34.942 --> 03:36.390
What are you doing here so early?

03:36.391 --> 03:40.311
Oh, he generously offered
to watch your sister.

03:40.312 --> 03:42.563
I have to go record that podcast today.

03:42.564 --> 03:43.689
- Oh.
- Remember?

03:43.690 --> 03:46.226
The one about life after suicide?

03:46.229 --> 03:47.604
Yeah.

03:47.607 --> 03:50.361
I think it's really great
that you're doing that, Mom.

03:50.364 --> 03:51.546
Thanks, sweetie.

03:51.549 --> 03:52.878
You're gonna be amazing, D.

03:52.881 --> 03:55.324
Well, I'll settle for not
saying anything stupid.

03:55.327 --> 03:57.828
Uh, as your daughter,
I agree with that plan.

03:57.829 --> 03:59.671
Brooke's here.

03:59.674 --> 04:00.998
Hey, we still on for playing that song

04:01.000 --> 04:02.541
at Theo's birthday party next week?

04:02.542 --> 04:03.765
Uh, you know it.

04:03.768 --> 04:06.044
And you better practice,
because I'm bringing my "A" game.

04:06.046 --> 04:07.672
Bye-bye, Charlie Farley!

04:12.179 --> 04:14.679
Y-You're sure Katherine's
okay with you watching Charlie?

04:14.680 --> 04:16.430
Totally.

04:16.430 --> 04:18.266
She's been so supportive.

04:18.267 --> 04:22.228
Somehow, some way, we're getting there.

04:22.229 --> 04:23.813
Okay.

04:23.814 --> 04:25.314
And...

04:25.315 --> 04:28.150
how is Andrew and his incredible coif?

04:28.151 --> 04:30.570
His coif is great. He says hello.

04:30.571 --> 04:33.531
He is using his day off
to hear me talk about

04:33.532 --> 04:35.283
the most painful moment of my life.

04:35.284 --> 04:38.744
So, yeah, I'd say
things are pretty good.

04:38.745 --> 04:40.492
Hey, you.

04:40.495 --> 04:42.748
Can you believe this
is where we are now?

04:45.252 --> 04:47.044
Actually, I can.

